19 people have now subscribed to the new TRUB mailing list.
40some have not yet responded to the "invitation".

We will have to figure out how some of the new features work - if you create an account for yourself at http://www.egroups.com you can read an archive of the mailing list via the web.

Another thing I have noticed is that the "Subject" line of all mail from the mailing list will start with "<TRUB>".

Information went out via US Mail several days ago on TRUB-X.  All dues-paid club members should get it.  I will also be posting the info tonight to http://trubx.home.mindspring.com.

-Gary Clayton
